OL,3,CHealth overspend sends Guernsey #2
OL,4,Cmillion over budget
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey is likely to go
OL,7,Fover budget by the end of the year due
OL,8,Fto overspending by the island's health
OL,9,Fdepartment.
OL,11,FThe government's budget for 2025 is
OL,12,Fexpected to be released next week,
OL,13,Fwith committees understood to have
OL,14,Funderspent their budgets by #4 million
OL,15,Fcollectively.
OL,17,FHowever, it was revealed in the States
OL,18,Fthat overspending from the Committee
OL,19,Ffor Health and Social Care (HSC) means
OL,20,Fthey could be #2 million over budget
OL,21,Fby the end of 2024.
