OL,3,CHealth overspend sends Guernsey #2
OL,4,Cmillion over budget
OL,6,FHSC is heading for an overspend of
OL,7,Faround #4.5 million by the end of the
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FReasons include the #30 million
OL,11,Fprojected overspend for the second
OL,12,Fhalf of the hospital build, and more
OL,13,Frecently the committee's flagship IT
OL,14,Fproject going over budget by #5
OL,15,Fmillion.
OL,17,FGuernsey's government has now
OL,18,Fintroduced a new system for A&E costs
OL,19,Fon Tuesday 1 October.
