OL,3,CHealth overspend sends Guernsey #2
OL,4,Cmillion over budget
OL,6,FThe system would see increased charges
OL,7,Ffor patients receiving emergency
OL,8,Fhospital treatment in an attempt to
OL,9,Fintroduce a 'consistent' structure for
OL,10,Ffees.
OL,12,FPresident for HSC, Deputy Al Brouard,
OL,13,Fdefended increased charges and the
OL,14,Foverspend, saying that there has been
OL,15,Fa 9% increase in the number of people
OL,16,Fusing A&E services.
