OL,3,CHealth overspend sends Guernsey #2
OL,4,Cmillion over budget
OL,6,FHe explains: "We need the doctors, the
OL,7,Ffacilities, this all needs to be up to
OL,8,Fdate. So I think being within a few
OL,9,Fper cent of our budget I think is
OL,10,Fpretty good going, given the times
OL,11,Fwe're living in."
OL,13,FNew charges mean that adults now pay
OL,14,Fup to #250 for hospital assessment and
OL,15,Ftreatment, with under 18s paying no
OL,16,Fmore than #25.
OL,18,FJersey and UK residents - as well as
OL,19,Fcancer patients - are exempt from new
OL,20,Fcharges.
